g.text: This study was performedin the framework of bilateral French-Lithuanian program“Gilibert”
19981WG/2009/2010), supported by Research Council of Lithuania (grant no. TAP-47/2010 and
TAP-11/2010) and the French Research Minister.
C.R. and T.T. conceived the study, C.E.-K., P.R.V., C.R. and T.T. designed the experiments,
B.Z., O.M. and C.E.-K. conducted the experiments, C.R., P.R.V., C.E.-K., B.Z., O.M. and T.T. analyzed the results,
B.Z. and C.E.-K. wrote the manuscript, P.R.V. and T.T. acquired the funding.
The authors declare no conﬂict of interest.
